info.title: F5 Distributed Cloud Services API for ves.io.schema.shape.safeap
info.description:
Use this API to interact with SAFE Account Protection endpoints.
All calls which not include user interaction allow a blob as the payload and return a CubeJS Structure as the return parameter.
